---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'May 1, 2026';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — AllStar Martial Arts"
  description="How AllStar Martial Arts in Union, NJ collects, uses, and protects your information."
  noindex={false}
>
  <section class="section-pad bg-white">
    <div class="container-page max-w-3xl">
      <div class="eyebrow">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl text-brand-black mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose-style space-y-5 text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          AllStar Martial Arts ("we", "us", "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect the information you provide when you visit our website, fill out a form, contact us, or sign up for the free trial.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you fill out a lead form, request a trial, or contact us, we may collect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Your name (first and last)</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Mobile phone number</li>
          <li>Program of interest</li>
          <li>Any message or comments you choose to send us</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not collect payment information through this website. Membership payments are handled in person at the gym.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information you provide to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Respond to your inquiry and confirm your free trial</li>
          <li>Send you appointment reminders, follow-up messages, and class information</li>
          <li>Send periodic updates and offers related to AllStar Martial Arts (you can opt out at any time)</li>
          <li>Improve the website and our customer service</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">3. SMS and Phone Communications</h2>
        <p>
          By providing your mobile phone number and opting in via our forms, you consent to receive SMS text messages and calls from AllStar Martial Arts related to your inquiry, trial, scheduling, and ongoing membership communications. <strong>Message and data rates may apply.</strong> Message frequency varies. Reply <strong>STOP</strong> at any time to unsubscribe from text messages. Reply <strong>HELP</strong> for assistance.
        </p>
        <p>Your phone number and SMS opt-in data will <strong>not</strong> be shared with third parties or affiliates for their marketing purposes.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">4. How We Share Your Information</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Service providers</strong> who help us operate the business (e.g. SMS, email, scheduling, hosting)</li>
          <li><strong>Legal authorities</strong> when required by law</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">5. Cookies & Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          Our website may use cookies and basic analytics tools to understand how visitors use the site. You can disable cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies will not block your ability to use the site or fill out forms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">6. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We use reasonable measures to protect the information you provide. No system is 100% secure, but we work to safeguard your data against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may request to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Review the information we have on file for you</li>
          <li>Correct or update your information</li>
          <li>Delete your information from our records</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To make any of these requests, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@allstarbjj.com" class="text-brand-navy underline">info@allstarbjj.com</a>.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our services are intended for adults and parents inquiring about classes for their children. We do not knowingly collect personal information directly from children under 13. Parents and guardians provide all information about minors.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top reflects the most recent changes. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl text-brand-black mt-8 mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this Privacy Policy? Contact us:
        </p>
        <p class="bg-brand-gray-light p-5 rounded-md text-sm not-italic">
          <strong>AllStar Martial Arts</strong><br/>
          1166 West Chestnut St, Union, NJ 07083<br/>
          📞 <a href="tel:+19086412769" class="text-brand-navy underline">(908) 641-2769</a><br/>
          ✉️ <a href="mailto:info@allstarbjj.com" class="text-brand-navy underline">info@allstarbjj.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .prose-style :global(h2) { font-family: 'Roboto Condensed', Impact, sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; }
</style>
